query:
SELECT json_agg(
			json_build_object(
				'date', date,
				'mod_id', mod_id,
				'author_id', author_id::text,
				'downloads_total', downloads_total,
				'views', views,
				'followers', followers,
				'favorited', favorited,
				'vote_data', json_build_object(
					'votes_up', votes_up,
					'votes_down', votes_down,
					'score', score
				),
				'num_comments', num_comments,
				'playtime', playtime,
				'time_updated', time_updated,
				'version', version
			)
			ORDER BY date DESC
		) AS "history: Value"
		FROM mod_history
		WHERE author_id = $1
